{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Hashed string"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String\/sdbmhash"},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdbmhash","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This algorithm was created for sdbm (a public-domain reimplementation of ndbm) database library.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"it was found to do well in scrambling bits, causing better distribution of the keys and fewer splits.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"it also happens to be a good general hashing function with good distribution.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the actual function is hash(i) = hash(i - 1) * 65599 + str[i];","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"what is included below is the faster version used in gawk.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[there is even a faster, duff-device version] the magic prime constant 65599 (2^6 + 2^16 - 1)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"was picked out of thin air while experimenting with many different constants.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this is one of the algorithms used in berkeley db (see sleepycat) and elsewhere.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string\/sdbmhash"]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sdbmhash"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"SwiftExtras","relatedModules":["Swift"]}],"title":"sdbmhash","externalID":"s:SS11SwiftExtrasE8sdbmhashSivp","extendedModule":"Swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras","doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift","doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift/String/sdbmhash":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"sdbmhash","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Hashed string","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String\/sdbmhash","url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string\/sdbmhash","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdbmhash","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift/String":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string","role":"symbol","abstract":[],"fragments":[{"text":"extension","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"String","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"String","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras":{"url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras","type":"topic","title":"SwiftExtras","kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras","role":"collection"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift","identifier":